            				<header class='rail-article-titles'>
            					<h1 class='h5'>Philistines</h1>
            					<address class='p'>By Nancy Lemann</address>
            					<time class='p'>February 23, 2024</time>
            				</header>
            			</a>
            		</article>
                                		<article class='rail-article'>
            			<a href='https://www.theparisreview.org/blog/?post_type=post&p=166830'>
